'''Sabri Ben Hessen''' ({{langx|ar|صبري بن حسن}}; born 13 June 1996) is a Tunisian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1]] club [[Étoile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]], and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].

==Club career==
Ben Hessen is a youth product of [[CS Sfaxien]], and signed his first professional contract with the club in 2013.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.winwin.com/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%B3-%D8%B5%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%AF-%D9%85%D8%BA%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%B3%D9%8A|title=الحارس صبري بن حسن يريد مغادرة النادي الصفاقسي}}</ref> On 14 June 2018, he extended his contract with CS Sfaxien until 2022 and joined [[CS Hammam-Lif]] on loan for the remainder of the season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nessma.tv/ar/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/actu/%D8%B1%D8%B3%D9%85%D9%8A-%D9%87%D9%8A%D8%A6%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%B3%D9%8A-%D8%AA%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%B3-%D8%B5%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%D8%A5%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%87%D9%85%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%A7-8249/69270|title=رسمي:: هيئة النادي الصفاقسي تعير الحارس صبري بن حسن إلى الهمهاما|date=14 January 2018|website=www.nessma.tv}}</ref> On 28 June 2022, he extended his contract with CS Sfaxien until 2024.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jawharafm.net/ar/article/%D8%B5%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%AC%D8%AF%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B4%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%B3%D9%8A/96/220337?fbclid=IwAR3LGxo36NR1RcRov8KbEr9WsVRteNSLaUJoc6S7WREJn-AgHJAwsXrA2lE|title=صبري بن حسن يجدد المشوار مع النادي الصفاقسي|website=JawharaFM}}</ref> On 5 February 2024, he again extended his contract until 2027.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mosaiquefm.net/ar/%D8%AA%D9%88%D9%86%D8%B3-%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/1236830/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%B3%D9%8A-%D8%B5%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%D9%8A-%D8%AC%D8%AF-%D8%AF-%D8%B9%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%87-%D9%85%D8%B9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%81%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%82|title=النادي الصفاقسي: صبري بن حسن يُجدّد عقده مع الفريق|website=Mosaique FM}}</ref> On 2 August 2025, he transferred to [[Étoile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]] on a 3-year contract.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.assabahnews.tn/ar/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/127605-%D8%B5%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%82%D9%91%D8%B9-%D9%84%D9%84%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85|title=صبري بن حسن يوقّع للنجم|date=24 July 2025|website=جريدة الصباح نيوز}}</ref>

==International career==
Ben Hessen played for the [[Tunisia national under-17 football team|Tunisia U17]]s at the [[2013 FIFA U-17 World Cup]]. He played for the [[Tunisia national under-23 football team|Tunisia U23]]s at the [[2015 U-23 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ar.lemaghreb.tn/%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%B6%D8%A9/item/42743-%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%B3%D9%8A-%D8%B5%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D9%86-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%D9%84%D9%80%C2%AB%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A8%C2%BB-%D8%A7%D8%B4%D8%AA%D9%82%D8%AA-%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AC%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%AC%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D8%AD%D9%8A-%D9%83%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%81%D8%B1%D8%B5%D8%A9-%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B0%D9%88%D9%82-%D9%84%D8%B0%D8%A9-%C2%AB%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%84%D9%91%D9%85%D8%A9%C2%BB-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%A9|title=جريدة المغرب &#124; حارس النادي الصفاقسي صبري بن حسن لـ«المغرب»: اشتقت لأجواء الملاعب والحجر الصحي كان فرصة لتذوق لذة «اللّمة» العائلية|first=وسام بن عبد|last=الله|website=ar.lemaghreb.tn}}</ref> He made the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]] for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://assarih.com/%d9%82%d8%a7%d8%a6%d9%85%d8%a9-%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%85%d9%86%d8%aa%d8%ae%d8%a8-%d9%81%d9%8a-%d9%83%d8%a3%d8%b3-%d8%a3%d9%85%d9%85-%d8%a7%d9%81%d8%b1%d9%8a%d9%82%d9%8a%d8%a7/|title=قائمة المنتخب في كأس أمم افريقيا}}</ref> He made his official debut with the senior team in a 1–0 friendly win over [[Haiti national football team|Haiti]] on 28 March 2026.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mundodeportivo.com/futbol/internacional/20260329/1004161422/0-1-tunez-impone-rocosa-haiti.html|title=0-1: Túnez se impone a una rocosa Haití|date=29 March 2026|website=Mundo Deportivo}}</ref> He made the final squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/cy42jjj4gg4o|title=Tunisia boss Sabri Lamouchi leaves Ferjani Sassi out of World Cup squad|date=15 May 2026|website=BBC Sport}}</ref>

